Dealing with acne-prone skin has always been a part of my journey & I’ve now realized how important it is to find the *right cleanser* that cleanses well and does not strip off the skin! (AD) 

That’s why I’ve been loving @novologyofficial’s Acne Cleanser! ✨ Co-created with dermatologists, it’s powered by TT2 Technology which targets acne-causing bacteria while protecting your skin’s microbiome.💧

With key ingredients like Thymol to reduce inflammation 🔬 and Terpineol to soothe irritation 🌿, it’s lightweight, non-drying and super gentle. The best part? It’s clinically proven to reduce acne in just 6 washes over 3 days. My skin feels balanced, calm and cared for like never before. 🫶
